mappings.messageTemplate:
Fireflies webhook received. A new meeting transcript is ready.

Webhook payload: {{json}}

Use the Fireflies API to fetch the full transcript using the meetingId. Then extract: decisions, action items (with owners and deadlines), blockers, scope changes, and open questions. Write the structured meeting note to the Meeting Notes database in Notion. Create a task for each action item via the task-handler skill (the Sprint Board is RETIRED — do NOT write to it). Post a summary to Slack.
